// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0488 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: caca60f7-4fe3-5de1-ba68-6c4a19677ae0

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04-ESM*")
